Took the viewport screenshot and saved it as /tmp/playwright/-tmp-cal-diy-setup.png

### Ran Playwright code
```js
// Screenshot viewport and save it as /tmp/playwright/-tmp-cal-diy-setup.png
await page.screenshot({
path: '/tmp/playwright/-tmp-cal-diy-setup.png',
  scale: 'css',
  type: 'png'
});
```

